Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.08,0:22:00.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}诶
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.19,0:22:03.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}给我以最快速度离开这座城市
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.48,0:22:07.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}你对欧塔斯的黑暗一无所知
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.38,0:22:10.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}欧塔斯的 黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.09,0:22:19.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}你只需要这样做
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.13,0:22:21.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}世界就会被拯救
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.67,0:22:27.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}没错 拯救世界的正是你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.36,0:22:29.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8}巫拉
